    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"page90R_mcid15\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">Fuma Clansmen are expected to </span><span dir=\"ltr\">predict the trajectory of an attack long before they eve</span><span dir=\"ltr\">n draw </span><span dir=\"ltr\">their weapon, allowing them to bounce attacks off of </span><span dir=\"ltr\">unsuspecting surfaces. <br />Beginning at 3rd level, twice per short </span><span dir=\"ltr\">rest, when you would miss a ranged weapon, or taijutsu </span><span dir=\"ltr\">attack that uses a weapon with the Thrown Property, you can </span><span dir=\"ltr\">remake the attack</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">roll, taking the second result.</span></span></p>",
